- 'Active' contracts are those with a contract status of 'Active';
- 'Defensive and physical stats' include marking, standing tackle, sliding tackle, pace, shooting, passing, dribbling, defending, and physical;
- 'Contract details' include contract length, start and end dates, value, and status.

